sub_title: Co-Founder and Executive Producer at BALBOA FILMS
summary:
I’ve been a creative and supportive leader all my life. From directing the first theater plays organized by my high school, becoming the Photography Club President at Glendale Community College(USA), and being the Co-Owner, executive producer, and Director of a recognized film production company in Guayaquil, Ecuador named Balboa Films. 

Now, I'm looking forward to meet learn about the local media industry and experience a new culture that will have a deep influence in my future goals as a media professional. I have a lot to share and a great passion to work in creative and challenging environment.
